Package com.cyberfront.crdt.sample.data

Class SimpleInteger

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyberfront.crdt.sample.data.AbstractDataType
      • com.cyberfront.crdt.sample.data.SimpleInteger
  • public class SimpleInteger
extends AbstractDataType
    This is a concrete class type derived from AbstractDataType used to test the CRDT. It manages a Integer integerValue as its extension to the base type
